<h2 id="natalia-sálomon">Natalia Sálomon</h2>
<p>Type@Cooper Display Type Class of Summer 2020</p>

<h4 id="about-natalia">About Natalia</h4>
<p>Natalia is a Colombian designer based in the US. She works between sculpture, product, graphic, and primarily landscape design.  She is inspired by the role and scale of type in public gardens.</p>

